$ ~/.thunderbird/abcd5678_default.default/logins.json

Apparently, this file stores login data and, in encrypted form, → development/security/password[passwords].
The keys to decrypt the encrypted passwords are stored in → Linux/fhs/home/username/_thunderbird/abcd5678_default/key4_db.

